name: American Apparel High Waist Jeans (Medium Wash)
description:
Size 26.Worn once Perfect Condition. I have something similar thats why I'm switching.

-Online description-
Introducing American Apparel Jeans! A classic style and wash unlike anything else that's been on the market for the last 15 years. Our High-Waist Jean is made from 100% cotton, 14 oz. denim. A heavyweight, non-stretch jean you can wear and wear to get that perfect, broken-in fit and feel. Hitting just above the belly button, these jeans will suck you in and smooth you out. They should fit nice and tight upon first wear and will loosen up after just a few hours, then return to their original size when washed. Order a size down for a snug fit, or to get a more relaxed feel order the same size as your waist measurement. Laundered for reduced shrinkage. Made in the USA. 

• Denim (100% Cotton) construction • Metal zipper and button closure • 5-pocket style • Classic belt loops
